\begin_layout Subsection
Project Stakeholders
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Stakeholders are individuals or organizations that are actively involved
 or whose interest may be affected by the execution of the project.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The may also exert influence over the project’s objectives and outcome.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The Project Management team must:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
